Despite the "imminent demonstrator", students must study, create projects and spend their final exams.
In the state of Pennsylvania, the final exam will be passed on the eve of the Apocalypse, which does not leave students any choice but to work "until the very night of the supposed world end," Restall said.
The courses have proved to be quite popular.
